{
  "texts": [
    "The 3D input covers 3D scene and segmented objects.",
    "Our 3D perceiver contains frozen 3D scene encoder and 3D object encoder, trainable attributes encoder and projectors.",
    "We construct 3D vision-language prompt with system message, 3D features and task instructions.",
    "Leveraging the 3D prompt, we can fine-tune LLM efficiently by Lora to solve 3D tasks.",
    "the coordinate of center x, y, z and its length, width and height."
  ]
}